设置permission，feature：
readPermissionsFromXml(/etc/permissions/ *.xml)@ApplicationPackageManager.java


获取feature：
packageManager.getSystemAvailableFeatures-->mPM.getSystemAvailableFeatures
@ApplicationPackageManager.java-->getSystemAvailableFeatures-->mAvailableFeatures
@ApplicationPackageManager.java


//notLowRam="true" 非低内存启动功能
<feature name="android.software.voice_recognizers" notLowRam="true" />

frameworks/base/core/java/android/app/ApplicationPackageManager.java
